<title>Paṇāmagāthā - Sūrassatinīti - Nīti-gantha-saṅgaho - Anya</title>
</metadata>
<body>
<centered line="1">Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</centered>
<book line="2">Sūrassatīnīti</book>
<subhead line="3">Paṭhamo bhāgo</subhead>
<chapter line="4">Paṇāmagāthā</chapter>
<hangnum line="5" number="1"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="6">Mukhamhā <pageBreak edition="M" number="1.0001" />bhagavantassa,</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="7">Sugandhakamalā subhā;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="8">Sañjātaṃ uttamaṃ vāṇiṃ,</gatha3>
<gathalast line="9">Vandāmi vittamānasā.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="10" number="2"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="11">Samajjhiṭṭho racissāmi,</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="12">Dakkhena rājamantinā;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="13">Nāmena santena,</gatha3>
<gatha2 line="14">Nītiṃ lokahitāvahaṃ;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="15">Sālaṅkāraṃ sopadesaṃ,</gatha3>
<gathalast line="16">Nāmenāhaṃ svarassatiṃ.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="17" number="3"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="18">Pekkhantvimaṃ nītiṃ santā,</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="19">Mañjūsarukkhasannibhaṃ;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="20">Nānopadesasaṃpuṇṇaṃ,</gatha3>
<gathalast line="21">Sadatthakusalā sadā.</gathalast>
